research_municipality_step.notes: Information was gathered from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, the City of Hale Center's official website, and the Texas State Directory Online. There was a minor discrepancy regarding the Mayor Pro Tem role in one source, but the majority of recent sources indicate Julio De La Garza holds this position in addition to being a Council Member. No specific ward, district, precinct, position, seat, place, or post designations were found for the council members; therefore, designations are listed as an empty array.
